---

**4. `.env` should be in `.gitignore`**

You committed your `.env` file into the zip. You must make sure `.env` is gitignored so real secrets never end up in version control. Create a `.gitignore` at the root:
```
.env
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
.pytest_cache/
.mypy_cache/
.ruff_cache/
dist/
*.egg-info/